import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['net_generation'])
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title("What is the trend of net generation over the years?", wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    data_pivot = data.pivot_table(index='year', columns='source', values='net_generation', aggfunc='sum')
    data_pivot.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True, ax=plt.gca())
    
    plt.title("What is the distribution of net generation by source?")
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Net Generation')
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    avg_net_generation = data.groupby('source')['net_generation'].mean()
    avg_net_generation.plot(kind='bar')
    
    plt.xlabel('Source')
    plt.ylabel('Average Net Generation')
    plt.title('What is the average net generation by source?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    total_net_generation_by_source = data.groupby('source')['net_generation'].sum()
    plt.pie(total_net_generation_by_source, labels=total_net_generation_by_source.index, autopct='%1.1f%%')
    
    plt.title("What is the total net generation by source?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
